# MLObjectDetector.ModelParameters.FeatureExtractorType

**Enumeration**

The underlying base model that extracts image features for an object-detector training session.

## Declaration

```swift
enum FeatureExtractorType
```

## Designating a feature extractor

- **MLObjectDetector.ModelParameters.FeatureExtractorType.objectPrint(revision:)**: A feature extractor you use with a transfer-learning algorithm for object detectors.

## Supporting types

- **MLObjectDetector.ModelParameters.ValidationData**: A validation dataset for an object detector.
- **MLObjectDetector.ModelParameters.ModelAlgorithmType**: An object-detector training algorithm.
